comments: Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Beal (PHX) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) is moving alongside Durant's (PHX) path as he slides his forearm off Durant's side on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Gordon (DEN) legally contests Durant's (PHX) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Both O'Neale (PHX) and Jokic (DEN) come together off-ball where they briefly engage before separating.
O'Neale (PHX) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (PHX) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jokic (DEN) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Gordon (DEN) legally contests Durant's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Beal (PHX) extends his arms forward when he initiates contact with Murray's (DEN) arm and affects Murray's SQBR.
O'Neale (PHX) moves alongside Jokic's (DEN) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt.
Replay review confirms that the game clock had expired before the put-back shot attempt by Gordon (DEN).
